wiki.text:
'Extent' has several meanings: *Extent (file systems), a contiguous region of
computer storage medium reserved for a file *The period during which a
variable has a particular value *Extent, a technical description of the
wingspan of a bird, bat, or other flying animal *Extent, a writ allowing a
creditor to seize or assume temporary ownership of a debtor's property; also,
the actual seizure in its execution *Extent, (English, archaic) an assessment
or valuation of property, usually for taxation. *Map extent, the portion of a
region shown in a map.
wiki.title: extent
